Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
selectModule(25.10)                                        selectModule(25.10)

Name
       selectModule - Selects the specified module

Syntax
       selectModule

        [-help]

       <name>

       Selects the specified module.

Parameters
       -help  Prints a brief description that includes type and default infor-
              mation for each selectModule parameter.

              For a detailed description of the command and all of its parame-
              ters, use the man command:

              man selectModule

       <name> Specifies the name of the module to be selected.

Example
       The following example selects the DTMF_INST module.

       selectModule DTMF_INST

Related Information
              * deselectModule

